戴維斯的紀念雕像矗立在厄尼•戴維斯中學(Ernie Davis Middle School)，該建築曾是戴維斯就讀的埃爾邁拉高中, 現在變更為一所中學並以戴維斯的名字命名。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.elmiracityschools.com/Davis.cfm/ |title=''Elmira City Schools.com'' Ernie Davis Middle School, March 24, 2014 |access-date=2014-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009175033/http://elmiracityschools.com/Davis.cfm |archive-date=2014-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>戴維斯的另一個雕像矗立在雪城大學的校園裡，靠近亨德里克斯教堂(Hendricks Chapel)。[[File:ErnieDavisMiddleSchool.JPG|thumb]]
